## Overview

OnPrem PDF API is designed for organizations that must not transmit or process
customer data in third-party cloud environments.

Typical use cases include:

- Insurance companies  
- Banks and financial institutions  
- ERP and internal business systems  
- Healthcare providers  
- Government and public sector systems  
- Any environment with strict data protection or compliance requirements  

---

## Key Features

- REST API for structured PDF generation  
- 100 % on-premise deployment  
- No internet connection required after installation  
- No data storage or tracking  
- No external API calls  
- Self-contained rendering engine  
- Optional admin interface with license management  

