## Installation

OnPrem PDF API runs entirely inside your own network and is intended for internal
use.

### System Requirements

- Linux server or virtual machine  
- Debian or Ubuntu (LTS recommended)  
- Minimum 2 GB RAM (4 GB recommended)  
- Minimum 1 CPU core (2 recommended)  


Detailed installation and deployment instructions are available at:
https://onprempdf.com/installation.html


